1
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:21,000
- Akihisa: ON A NIGHT
ILLUMINATED BY COUNTLESS STARS

2
00:00:21,083 --> 00:00:22,916
AND A FLEETING CRESCENT MOON,

3
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:25,166
I WAS BEING PRESSURED BY

4
00:00:25,250 --> 00:00:29,583
THE SUSPICIOUSLY SUPPORTIVE
GIRLS IN MY CLASS.

5
00:00:29,666 --> 00:00:33,750
- AKI, CAN WE DO IT?

6
00:00:33,833 --> 00:00:36,375
- AKIHISA, PLEASE.
I'M BEGGING YOU.

7
00:00:36,458 --> 00:00:38,125
PLEASE, CAN WE DO IT?

8
00:00:38,208 --> 00:00:40,875
- I'M SORRY, I CAN'T.

9
00:00:40,958 --> 00:00:43,791
- BUT WHY?
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

10
00:00:43,875 --> 00:00:46,083
- YOU MEAN, YOU DON'T WANT TO?

11
00:00:46,166 --> 00:00:49,000
- IT'S NOT THAT.
I JUST CAN'T.

12
00:00:49,083 --> 00:00:50,958
- WELL, THEN IF THAT'S
 WHAT YOU REALLY WANT,

13
00:00:51,041 --> 00:00:54,333
WE'LL JUST HAVE TO DO IT
WITH KOUTA INSTEAD.

14
00:00:54,416 --> 00:00:56,333
- OKAY?  AKI?

15
00:00:56,416 --> 00:01:00,041
- OKAY.  I'M COOL WITH THAT.

16
00:01:00,125 --> 00:01:02,958
- AWESOME!  KOUTA, DID YOU
HEAR WHAT AKI JUST TOLD US?

17
00:01:03,041 --> 00:01:06,125
YOU GET ONE MORE.
- AAH!

18
00:01:06,208 --> 00:01:08,000
- Fukuhara:
THIS IS CALLED ISHI-DAKI.

19
00:01:08,083 --> 00:01:10,416
IT'S A FORM OF TORTURE
USED IN THE EDO ERA.

20
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,666
- ( boys groaning, screaming )

21
00:01:11,750 --> 00:01:15,041
- AFFAIRS WILL NOT
BE PERMITTED.

22
00:01:15,125 --> 00:01:17,208
- NOW IT'S YOUR TURN
FOR MORE, AKIHISA.

23
00:01:17,291 --> 00:01:19,708
- Akihisa:
NO!

24
00:01:21,375 --> 00:01:22,958
- ( dog barking )

25
00:01:23,041 --> 00:01:25,083
- Fukuhara: WOW, THE GIRLS
 ARE KINDA BALLSY TONIGHT.

26
00:01:28,083 --> 00:01:30,458
- ( theme music playing )
- ( singing in Japanese )

27
00:02:56,083 --> 00:02:57,916
- Fukuhara:
EARLIER THAT MORNING...

28
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,750
THINGS GOT A BIT STRANGE.

29
00:03:00,833 --> 00:03:04,458
IT WAS THE DAY BEFORE
THEIR ACADEMIC TRAINING CAMP.

30
00:03:04,541 --> 00:03:07,416
AKIHISA RECEIVED
AN ANONYMOUS LETTER.

31
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,333
WITHIN IT WAS A MESSAGE--

32
00:03:09,416 --> 00:03:13,291
A MESSAGE THAT WOULD BLOW
OUR LITTLE ANTI-HERO'S MIND.

33
00:03:13,375 --> 00:03:15,125
- ( Akihisa's voice )
"DEAR AKIHISA,

34
00:03:15,208 --> 00:03:16,083
I KNOW YOUR SECRET"?

35
00:03:17,791 --> 00:03:19,625
WHY WOULD SOMEONE DO THIS TO ME?

36
00:03:19,708 --> 00:03:21,125
- WHAT'S WRONG, AKIHISA?

37
00:03:21,208 --> 00:03:22,500
YOU SEEM KINDA BUMMED OUT
THIS MORNING.

38
00:03:22,583 --> 00:03:24,916
- HUH?  WHAT?!
NO, NOTHING'S WRONG.

39
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,583
- WHY ARE YOU ACTING WEIRD
THIS TIME?

40
00:03:26,666 --> 00:03:28,791
AND WHAT'S BEHIND YOUR BACK?
- MY BACK?  WHAT?

41
00:03:28,875 --> 00:03:30,291
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

42
00:03:30,375 --> 00:03:32,041
- OKAY.  YOU MUST BE 
HIDING A LOVE LETTER.

43
00:03:32,125 --> 00:03:33,500
YEAH?

44
00:03:33,583 --> 00:03:35,291
- WHY WOULD YOU EVER
SAY SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

45
00:03:35,375 --> 00:03:36,833
YOU KNOW HOW THESE GUYS GET.

46
00:03:36,916 --> 00:03:39,208
- BESIDES THAT, WHO WOULD
GIVE YOU A LOVE LETTER?

47
00:03:39,291 --> 00:03:40,916
TALK ABOUT RIDICULOUS.

48
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,375
- TALK ABOUT YOUR FACE!

49
00:03:42,458 --> 00:03:44,833
PEOPLE SEND ME LETTERS.
TAKE TODAY--

50
00:03:47,291 --> 00:03:48,583
- NEXT TIME YOU'RE DEAD.

51
00:03:48,666 --> 00:03:50,500
- PLEASE FORGIVE ME,
MISS MINAMI.

52
00:03:50,583 --> 00:03:52,416
- NOW WHY DON'T YOU TRY
TELLING THE TRUTH FOR ONCE?

53
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:55,083
- ALL RIGHT! I WAS HIDING
A LETTER FROM YOU.  IT WAS BL--

54
00:03:55,166 --> 00:03:57,083
WAIT, I DON'T THINK
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO TELL PEOPLE

55
00:03:57,166 --> 00:03:58,333
WHEN YOU'RE GETTING BLACKMAILED.

56
00:03:58,416 --> 00:04:00,500
THE BAD GUYS ALWAYS SAY
NOT TO ON TV.

57
00:04:00,583 --> 00:04:02,666
- "BLA--" WHAT?
- WHAT "BLA--" WHAT?

58
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:04,500
- Fukuhara:
WHEN HUMANS ARE IN STRESS MODE,

59
00:04:04,583 --> 00:04:06,458
THEIR SYNAPSES FIRE RANDOMLY,

60
00:04:06,541 --> 00:04:08,125
CAUSING A SCATTERED
THOUGHT PATTERN.

61
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:10,375
THIS IS CALLED
A KALEIDOSCOPE OF MEMORIES.

62
00:04:10,458 --> 00:04:14,250
- YES!  UH, BLACK COMPETITIVE
SWIMWEAR SOCIETY INVITATION

63
00:04:14,333 --> 00:04:16,583
WAS WHAT I WAS HIDING.
- WHAT?

64
00:04:16,666 --> 00:04:19,416
- Fukuhara: AKIHISA HAD
WATCHED A DOCUMENTARY CALLED,

65
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:23,041
"COMPETITIVE SWIMMER: 24-HOUR
CLOSE-UP" THE NIGHT BEFORE.

66
00:04:23,125 --> 00:04:26,041
- OKAY, SO ARE YOU GONNA GO?
- MAYBE!  YES.  I DON'T KNOW...

67
00:04:26,125 --> 00:04:28,375
I THINK THEY'RE COOL.
- ( sighs ) JEEZ.

68
00:04:28,458 --> 00:04:31,916
- OH, CRAP. I'M GETTING CLOSE TO
THAT POINT OF NO RETURN THING.

69
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,875
- WHAT DO YOU FIND SO COOL 
ABOUT COMPETITIVE SWIMMERS?

70
00:04:34,958 --> 00:04:36,875
- HUH?  UH...

71
00:04:36,958 --> 00:04:38,375
THINK, AKI.
WHAT MAKES THEM COOL?

72
00:04:38,458 --> 00:04:40,791
I LIKE WHAT THEY WEAR.

73
00:04:40,875 --> 00:04:44,458
PERFECT!  NOW I SOUND
LIKE A TOTAL WEIRDO!

74
00:04:44,541 --> 00:04:47,125
- MINAMI, EVERYTHING
HE JUST SAID WAS A LIE.

75
00:04:47,208 --> 00:04:49,416
- WHAT? THAT STUPID STORY
SOUNDED SO REAL,

76
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:51,125
I ALMOST BELIEVED HIM.

77
00:04:52,291 --> 00:04:53,875
IF YOU DON'T TELL ME
THE TRUTH THIS TIME,

78
00:04:53,958 --> 00:04:55,708
YOU'RE GONNA PAY.
SPIT IT OUT, JERKY!

79
00:04:55,791 --> 00:04:59,416
- OKAY.  I MIGHT HAVE GOTTEN
A BLACKMAIL NOTE THIS MORNING.

80
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:01,458
- AH!  WELL, THAT'S A RELIEF.

81
00:05:01,541 --> 00:05:03,541
- WHAT DOES THIS
"MIGHT BE A BLACKMAIL NOTE" SAY?

82
00:05:03,625 --> 00:05:06,583
- OH.  "STOP TRYING TO GET
CLOSER TO THE GIRLS

83
00:05:06,666 --> 00:05:09,250
WHO ARE ALWAYS AROUND YOU
OR ELSE."  THAT'S ALL.

84
00:05:09,333 --> 00:05:11,125
- WHOA.  IF YOU ASK ME,
IT SOUNDS LIKE

85
00:05:11,208 --> 00:05:13,166
THE BLACKMAILER
IS JEALOUS OF YOU.

86
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:14,250
- AND IF YOU THINK ABOUT IT,

87
00:05:14,333 --> 00:05:15,916
THERE ARE ONLY TWO GIRLS
IN THIS CLASS.

88
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,125
HIMEJI AND HIDEYOSHI.

89
00:05:18,208 --> 00:05:20,541
WHOEVER IT IS MUST NOT
LIKE ONE OF THEM.

90
00:05:20,625 --> 00:05:22,458
- YOU DO REALIZE SHE
MOST LIKELY JUST LEFT

91
00:05:22,541 --> 00:05:24,000
TO GO GET A METAL BAT, RIGHT?

92
00:05:24,083 --> 00:05:25,708
- WHY?!  I THOUGHT THAT WAS
A GOOD GUESS.

93
00:05:25,791 --> 00:05:27,291
- HOLD ON JUST A SECOND.

94
00:05:27,375 --> 00:05:29,458
WHAT ARE YOU BEING
BLACKMAILED WITH ANYWAY?

95
00:05:29,541 --> 00:05:30,750
- UH, I'M NOT REALLY SURE.

96
00:05:30,833 --> 00:05:33,583
"IF YOU REFUSE
TO HEED MY WARNING,

97
00:05:33,666 --> 00:05:35,541
I'LL RELEASE THESE PICTURES."

98
00:05:35,625 --> 00:05:37,916
COOL, THERE'S PICTURES!

99
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,125
- HEY, THOSE ARE FROM THE LAST
 SCHOOL FESTIVAL, AREN'T THEY?

100
00:05:40,208 --> 00:05:41,833
- BUT WHO TOOK THESE?

101
00:05:41,916 --> 00:05:44,208
SURELY THEY WON'T HAVE
ANYTHING CRAZIER THAN THIS.

102
00:05:46,541 --> 00:05:48,041
IT'S TRUNKS, SO IT'S OKAY.
IT'S TRUNKS, SO IT'S OKAY.

103
00:05:48,125 --> 00:05:49,333
IT'S TRUNKS, SO IT'S OKAY.
JUST TRUNKS!

104
00:05:49,416 --> 00:05:51,958
- EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT
OVER THERE?

105
00:05:52,041 --> 00:05:54,958
- YEAH, THERE'S REALLY NOTHING
THAT BAD IN THESE PICTURES.

106
00:05:55,041 --> 00:05:55,916
I THINK.

107
00:05:58,250 --> 00:06:00,083
NO!

108
00:06:00,166 --> 00:06:01,875
DON'T LOOK AT IT!
I'M HIDEOUS!

109
00:06:01,958 --> 00:06:03,625
I'VE NEVER BEEN SO ASHAMED!

110
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:05,500
- DUDE, YOU NEED TO CALM DOWN.
IT CAN'T BE THAT BAD.

111
00:06:05,583 --> 00:06:07,458
- IT CAN.

112
00:06:07,541 --> 00:06:09,333
THAT KIND OF POWER
IS DANGEROUS.

113
00:06:09,416 --> 00:06:11,583
WHAT EVIL VILLAIN
IS DOING THIS TO ME?

114
00:06:11,666 --> 00:06:13,416
- YOU'RE JUST BEING DRAMATIC.

115
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,750
EVERYONE WEARS
A FRENCH MAID COSTUME

116
00:06:14,833 --> 00:06:15,750
AT LEAST ONCE IN THEIR LIFE.

117
00:06:15,833 --> 00:06:17,375
- GOOD MORNING, YOU GUYS.

118
00:06:17,458 --> 00:06:19,041
LOVELY DAY, HUH?
HOW IS IT GOING?

119
00:06:19,125 --> 00:06:20,583
- YOU KNOW,
SAME OL', SAME OL'.

120
00:06:20,666 --> 00:06:22,166
- PERFECT TIMING.
WHY DON'T YOU SHOW

121
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:24,000
THOSE PICTURES TO HIMEJI,
SO SHE CAN PROVE

122
00:06:24,083 --> 00:06:25,250
THEY'RE NOT WORTH
FREAKING OUT ABOUT.

123
00:06:25,333 --> 00:06:26,958
- SHOW ME WHAT PICTURES?

124
00:06:27,041 --> 00:06:29,750
- OKAY, WHAT WOULD YOU DO
IF YOU SAW A PICTURE OF AKI

125
00:06:29,833 --> 00:06:31,083
DRESSED UP IN A MAID COSTUME?

126
00:06:31,166 --> 00:06:32,583
- WELL, FIRST OF ALL,

127
00:06:32,666 --> 00:06:34,208
I WOULD PROBABLY BUY A SCANNER.

128
00:06:34,291 --> 00:06:36,125
- HUH?
- THAT WAY, I WOULD BE ABLE

129
00:06:36,208 --> 00:06:37,666
TO DOWNLOAD THE IMAGE.

130
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,041
AND THEN SHARE AKIHISA'S CHARM

131
00:06:39,125 --> 00:06:40,583
WITH THE WORLD WIDE WEB.

132
00:06:40,666 --> 00:06:42,458
- DON'T JUMP, MAN!
IT'S NOT WORTH IT!

133
00:06:42,541 --> 00:06:44,833
- LET GO OF ME! I HAVE
NO REASON TO LIVE ANYMORE.

134
00:06:44,916 --> 00:06:47,625
- COME BACK INSIDE. LET'S GO
GET SOME ADVICE FROM KOUTA.

135
00:06:47,708 --> 00:06:50,458
- OF COURSE!  THAT IS
AN AWESOME PLAN, HIDEYOSHI.

136
00:06:50,541 --> 00:06:52,625
I WOULD EXPECT NOTHING LESS
FROM MY WIFE.

137
00:06:52,708 --> 00:06:55,041
- I THINK YOU MEAN HUSBAND?
- I THINK THEY'RE BOTH WRONG

138
00:06:55,125 --> 00:06:56,041
IN SO VERY MANY WAYS.

139
00:06:56,125 --> 00:06:58,000
- ( laughing )

140
00:06:58,083 --> 00:07:00,000
- Aki: OH, CRAP.

141
00:07:00,083 --> 00:07:01,416
THERE YOU ARE.

142
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:02,833
I HAVE A QUESTION
FOR YOU, KOUTA.

143
00:07:02,916 --> 00:07:04,250
- YEAH, WELL,
GET IN LINE, BUDDY.

144
00:07:04,333 --> 00:07:06,208
I WAS HERE FIRST.
- YOU NEED ADVICE TOO?

145
00:07:06,291 --> 00:07:08,375
- APPARENTLY, YUUJI
HAS A WEDDING SOON.

146
00:07:08,458 --> 00:07:10,708
- YEAH, WE ALL KNOW ABOUT THAT.
WHAT'S HE GONNA DO?

147
00:07:10,791 --> 00:07:12,750
I HAVE BIGGER PROBLEMS.
PEOPLE ARE ABOUT TO THINK

148
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:15,416
I'M A SICKO FREAK WHO ENJOYS
DRESSING UP LIKE A GIRL!

149
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:17,625
- SO WHAT?!  PEOPLE ALREADY KNOW
YOU'RE A SICKO FREAK.

150
00:07:17,708 --> 00:07:19,166
- SHUT UP AND GO BACK
TO YOUR WIFE.

151
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:20,750
GETTING MARRIED
HAS MADE YOU SUCK!

152
00:07:20,833 --> 00:07:22,625
- LIKE THE WORDS OF A PERVERT
ARE GONNA HURT ME?

153
00:07:22,708 --> 00:07:25,000
WHY DON'T YOU GO BACK TO WEARING
YOUR BIG SISTER'S CLOTHES?

154
00:07:25,083 --> 00:07:26,500
- ( both growling )

155
00:07:26,583 --> 00:07:29,666
( crying )

156
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:32,125
- YOU GUYS ARE SO SENSITIVE.
YOU JUST CAN'T TAKE TRASH TALK.

157
00:07:32,208 --> 00:07:36,291
- SO BACK TO ME... I MANAGED 
TO GET THIS AWAY FROM SHOUKO.

158
00:07:36,375 --> 00:07:38,875
IF I WIN THE TOURNAMENT, 
I'M GONNA PROPOSE TO YOU.

159
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:42,625
I LOVE YOU, SHOUKO!
- HUH?

160
00:07:42,708 --> 00:07:45,083
- Fukuhara: THESE ARE THE
WORDS AKIHISA AND HIDEYOSHI

161
00:07:45,166 --> 00:07:48,333
FABRICATED AT THE FUMIZUKI
ACADEMY SCHOOL FESTIVAL.

162
00:07:48,416 --> 00:07:49,916
- ( laughs nervously )

163
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,875
THAT SHOUKO CRACKS ME UP.

164
00:07:51,958 --> 00:07:54,291
WHO WOULD HAVE FIGURED SHE'D
WANT THOSE WORDS RECORDED?

165
00:07:54,375 --> 00:07:56,541
- I WOULD!
SHE'S GONNA PLAY IT FOR HER DAD

166
00:07:56,625 --> 00:07:58,000
AS PROOF OF OUR ENGAGEMENT.

167
00:07:58,083 --> 00:07:59,750
- OH.

168
00:07:59,833 --> 00:08:01,458
- SHE COULDN'T DO THIS HERSELF.

169
00:08:01,541 --> 00:08:03,250
SHE'S AN IDIOT WHEN IT COMES
TO TECHNICAL STUFF.

170
00:08:03,333 --> 00:08:04,791
WHICH MEANS THERE'S GOTTA BE
SOMEONE ELSE BEHIND THIS.

171
00:08:04,875 --> 00:08:06,333
- WHAT DID YOU
WANNA TALK ABOUT, AKI?

172
00:08:06,416 --> 00:08:08,500
- I DON'T KNOW ANY OTHER WAY
TO SAY THIS.

173
00:08:08,583 --> 00:08:10,583
AN UNDERWEAR PICTURE OF ME
IN A MAID'S COSTUME

174
00:08:10,666 --> 00:08:12,666
IS ABOUT TO HIT THE INTERNET
BIG TIME!

175
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,583
- HMM?  HOW'D THAT HAPPEN?

176
00:08:14,666 --> 00:08:16,500
- WELL, IT'S KINDA LIKE THIS.

177
00:08:16,583 --> 00:08:17,500
BLAH BLAH BLAH.
BLAH BLAH BLAH BLAH BLAH BLAH.

178
00:08:17,583 --> 00:08:19,291
- YEAH YEAH YEAH.

179
00:08:19,375 --> 00:08:21,583
SO WHERE'S THE PICTURE?
- OH, YEAH, IT'S RIGHT HERE.

180
00:08:21,666 --> 00:08:23,833
- NO!
- NO WHAT?!

181
00:08:23,916 --> 00:08:26,625
- ( sighs )

182
00:08:26,708 --> 00:08:28,958
THE ANGLE IN THAT PIC
IS BETTER THAN THE ONE I TOOK.

183
00:08:29,041 --> 00:08:31,541
- AAH!
THERE'S A TRAITOR IN OUR MIDST.

184
00:08:31,625 --> 00:08:32,750
- OH, STOP FREAKING OUT.

185
00:08:32,833 --> 00:08:34,541
IT'S NOT LIKE I'M GIVING 'EM
AWAY FOR FREE.

186
00:08:34,625 --> 00:08:36,833
- SO WHAT?!
YOU MAKE MONEY OFF OF ME?

187
00:08:36,916 --> 00:08:40,250
- I SEE.  IT APPEARS THAT
AKI'S IN THE SAME BOAT I AM.

188
00:08:40,333 --> 00:08:42,916
- YES, YOU'RE BOTH VICTIMS
OF BLACKMAIL, WIRETAPPING,

189
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,666
AND SURVEILLANCE PHOTOS.
- KOUTA?

190
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:46,625
I'D LIKE FOR YOU TO INVESTIGATE.

191
00:08:46,708 --> 00:08:48,125
AS A REWARD, I'LL BRING
SOME DIRTY MAGAZINES

192
00:08:48,208 --> 00:08:49,375
THAT YOU CAN BORROW.

193
00:08:49,458 --> 00:08:51,125
- I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.
- AND I'LL LET YOU HAVE

194
00:08:51,208 --> 00:08:52,583
HALF OF MY NAUGHTY TREASURE
COLLECTION.

195
00:08:52,666 --> 00:08:54,083
- THIS IS EXTREMELY
NOT A PROBLEM.

196
00:08:54,166 --> 00:08:56,083
- ( bell tolls )

197
00:08:56,166 --> 00:08:57,750
- SO THAT'S ABOUT
WHAT YOU CAN EXPECT

198
00:08:57,833 --> 00:08:59,416
FROM ACADEMIC TRAINING CAMP.
- COOL!

199
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,375
WE GET TO GO TO THE UZUKI
HIGHLANDS THIS YEAR.

200
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:03,125
- WOW, THAT'S KINDA SWANKY
FOR CAMP.

201
00:09:03,208 --> 00:09:05,041
- I KNOW, RIGHT?
I'M SO EXCITED ABOUT IT!

202
00:09:05,125 --> 00:09:07,000
- AND FOR THE LAST TIME,
THERE ARE DIFFERENT

203
00:09:07,083 --> 00:09:08,583
MEETING PLACES PER CLASS,
SO DON'T SCREW IT UP.

204
00:09:08,666 --> 00:09:11,000
- CLASS "A" IS PROBABLY
GONNA GO BY A LIMOUSINE BUS

205
00:09:11,083 --> 00:09:12,833
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT.
- TOTALLY.

206
00:09:12,916 --> 00:09:14,666
AND CLASS "F" WILL GET STUCK
WITH A MICRO-BUS.

207
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:16,416
- SPARE SEATS ARE STANDING UP.

208
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:18,416
NO, PROBABLY IN THE TRUNK
OR IN A BIKE RACK.

209
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:21,666
- CLASS "F" HAS THE DISTINCTION
 OF MEETING UP AT THE CAMPSITE.

210
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:24,541
- WHAT?!  WE DON'T EVEN
GET TRANSPORTATION?!

211
00:09:24,625 --> 00:09:27,083
- Fukuhara:
LIFE JUST ISN'T FAIR.

212
00:09:30,791 --> 00:09:33,416
- NUH-UH, THAT'S NOT TRUE.
- I SWEAR!

213
00:09:35,958 --> 00:09:37,833
ARE WE THERE YET?

214
00:09:39,958 --> 00:09:42,333
( snoring )

215
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:48,583
- I'M BORED.
- HUH?

216
