00:17:26,791 --> 00:17:28,333
- YEAH, AND FOR THE RECORD,

433
00:17:28,416 --> 00:17:29,958
MY TA-TAS ARE NORMALLY BIGGER
THAN THEY ARE TODAY.

434
00:17:30,041 --> 00:17:31,875
- LYING DOESN'T HELP ANYTHING,
MINAMI.

435
00:17:31,958 --> 00:17:34,000
- ( groans )
LADIES, ATTACK THEM AT WILL!

436
00:17:34,083 --> 00:17:35,625
- ( girls grunting )

437
00:17:35,708 --> 00:17:37,791
- I TAKE IT BACK.
I DIDN'T MEAN IT, I SWEAR!

438
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:41,083
MY SPLEEN.
HEY!

439
00:17:41,166 --> 00:17:43,083
WE GOTTA GET OUT OF HERE!
OOH-HOO.

440
00:17:43,166 --> 00:17:47,083
- BAD... BOY.

441
00:17:47,166 --> 00:17:48,916
- ( groaning )
- OH, NO!

442
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,500
IT'S TOO LATE.
GUYS!

443
00:17:50,583 --> 00:17:51,500
WE'RE ALL DEAD!

444
00:17:51,583 --> 00:17:52,916
- IT'S TIME, AKIHISA.

445
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,416
- WE'RE GOING TO
TEACH YOU A LESSON.

446
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:56,875
- ( screams )

447
00:18:00,958 --> 00:18:03,791
- WELL, THAT WASN'T THE NICEST
OF ACCUSATIONS, WAS IT?

448
00:18:03,875 --> 00:18:05,833
I STILL CAN'T FIGURE OUT
WHY THEY TREATED ME

449
00:18:05,916 --> 00:18:07,291
LIKE A VICTIM, THOUGH.

450
00:18:07,375 --> 00:18:09,458
- THEY OVERREACTED TO
A MISUNDERSTANDING.

451
00:18:09,541 --> 00:18:11,250
WE HADN'T EVEN
PEEKED ON THEM YET.

452
00:18:11,333 --> 00:18:13,458
- THEIR CAMERA WASN'T
ONE OF MINE, BY THE WAY.

453
00:18:13,541 --> 00:18:15,625
- SHE CRUSHED THAT THING
WITH HER BARE HAND.

454
00:18:15,708 --> 00:18:18,250
- IF THEY'RE GONNA BE
LIKE THAT, THEN WHO CARES?

455
00:18:18,333 --> 00:18:19,458
- YOUR WORDS DON'T MAKE SENSE.

456
00:18:19,541 --> 00:18:20,875
- THEY'VE ALREADY MADE
US DO THE TIME,

457
00:18:20,958 --> 00:18:22,333
SO WE MIGHT AS WELL
COMMIT THE CRIME.

458
00:18:22,416 --> 00:18:24,250
- YOU DON'T MEAN--
- HELL YEAH!

459
00:18:24,333 --> 00:18:26,041
I'M GONNA PEEK ON THE GIRLS
TAKING BATHS FOR REAL.

460
00:18:26,125 --> 00:18:28,666
- YUUJI, IF YOU WANNA SEE
SHOUKO NAKED,

461
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:30,375
I'M SURE ALL YOU HAVE TO DO
IS ASK HER.

462
00:18:30,458 --> 00:18:32,000
- THAT'S NOT
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT!

463
00:18:32,083 --> 00:18:33,791
WOULD YOU SHUT UP?
I DON'T WANNA SEE HER NAKED.

464
00:18:33,875 --> 00:18:35,583
- THIS ISN'T ABOUT SHOUKO.
IT'S ABOUT FINDING

465
00:18:35,666 --> 00:18:37,416
THE BOOTY BURN MARK CULPRIT.
- THAT'S RIGHT.

466
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:40,458
AT FIRST I THOUGHT PEEKING ON
THEM WAS CROSSING THE LINE,

467
00:18:40,541 --> 00:18:42,041
BUT IF THEY'RE GONNA
BE LIKE THAT,

468
00:18:42,125 --> 00:18:43,958
THEN I SAY SCREW THE LINE!
I'M GONNA LOOK AT

469
00:18:44,041 --> 00:18:46,041
EVERY GIRL'S BUTT UNTIL
I FIND ONE WITH A BURN ON IT!

470
00:18:46,125 --> 00:18:48,250
- I RECOGNIZE THAT CAMERA
AND MICROPHONE.

471
00:18:48,333 --> 00:18:50,166
THEY'RE THE SAME ONES
USED BY THE BLACKMAILER.

472
00:18:50,250 --> 00:18:51,666
- GET OUTTA TOWN!

473
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:53,500
- SO THE BURNT BUTT GIRL WHO'S
BLACKMAILING YUUJI AND ME

474
00:18:53,583 --> 00:18:54,708
IS THE SAME PERSON

475
00:18:54,791 --> 00:18:55,708
WHO WAS PEEKING ON THE
GIRLS' CHANGING ROOM

476
00:18:55,791 --> 00:18:56,958
EVEN THOUGH THEY
THOUGHT IT WAS US.

477
00:18:57,041 --> 00:18:59,291
- THERE'S NO REASON TO HESITATE.
SHE SET US UP.

478
00:18:59,375 --> 00:19:01,750
- OKAY, I'M REALLY CONFUSED.

479
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,791
- THEIR BATHING TIME
IS IN 30 MINUTES.

480
00:19:05,875 --> 00:19:07,708
THEY'RE ON THE OTHER SIDE
OF THAT DOOR.

481
00:19:07,791 --> 00:19:10,125
- WE DON'T HAVE MUCH TIME.
 LET'S GET IN THERE, BOYS!

482
00:19:10,208 --> 00:19:11,833
- ( all shouting )

483
00:19:11,916 --> 00:19:13,541
- STOP IMMEDIATELY!

484
00:19:13,625 --> 00:19:16,083
NOW COME ON, YOU KNOW
YOU CAN'T GO IN THERE, GUYS.

485
00:19:16,166 --> 00:19:17,750
- ISN'T THAT
THE CHEMISTRY TEACHER?

486
00:19:17,833 --> 00:19:19,500
- WHO CARES?
JUST KNOCK HIM DOWN.

487
00:19:19,583 --> 00:19:21,250
- I'D REALLY RATHER YOU DIDN'T.

488
00:19:21,333 --> 00:19:23,875
I'M SUMMONING MY AVATAR!
SUMMON!

489
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:29,708
- NO WAY!
- AH, TERRIFIC, THIS IS NEW.

490
00:19:29,791 --> 00:19:32,708
- Fukuhara: LIKE PROBATIONARY
STUDENTS' AVATARS,

491
00:19:32,791 --> 00:19:34,125
THE TEACHERS' AVATARS
ARE ALSO CAPABLE

492
00:19:34,208 --> 00:19:36,416
OF PHYSICAL INTERFERENCE.

493
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:37,791
- WHATEVER, DUDE.

494
00:19:37,875 --> 00:19:39,833
WE'RE GONNA CRUSH YOU RIGHT
ALONG WITH YOUR AVATAR.

495
00:19:39,916 --> 00:19:42,041
- I'LL JUST KEEP RUNNING.
- NO, WAIT.

496
00:19:42,125 --> 00:19:43,458
BEFORE YOU GO,

497
00:19:43,541 --> 00:19:45,291
I NEED YOU TO TELL ME WHAT
YOUR CHEMISTRY SCORE WAS.

498
00:19:45,375 --> 00:19:47,916
- IF I HAD JUST ONE MORE POINT
ON MY TEST,

499
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:50,083
JUST ONE MORE POINT...
- YEAH, WHAT WOULD IT BE?

500
00:19:50,166 --> 00:19:52,666
- IT'D BE A TWO.

501
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:54,416
- GOOD TO KNOW.
KEEP RUNNING.

502
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:56,500
- IT'LL BE HARD TO WIN
IF YOU HAVE TO FIGHT HIM ALONE.

503
00:19:56,583 --> 00:19:59,791
I'LL STAY AND HELP YOU OUT.
- YOU'RE THE MAN, HIDEYOSHI.

504
00:19:59,875 --> 00:20:02,791
- Both: SUMMON!

505
00:20:02,875 --> 00:20:04,666
- ( Avatars grunting )

506
00:20:04,750 --> 00:20:07,291
- WELL, KOUTA, MY MAN,
LOOKS LIKE IT'S UP TO US--

507
00:20:07,375 --> 00:20:08,250
HEY, HE'S ALREADY GONE!

508
00:20:12,083 --> 00:20:13,791
- I DON'T THINK SO, KID.

509
00:20:13,875 --> 00:20:16,250
- WELL, IF IT ISN'T
MR. OOSHIMA,

510
00:20:16,333 --> 00:20:17,333
HEALTH AND P.E. TEACHER.

511
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:23,291
- GIVE IT UP ALREADY, TSUCHIYA.

512
00:20:23,375 --> 00:20:24,791
- NO, YOU GIVE IT UP.

513
00:20:24,875 --> 00:20:28,583
THIS ISN'T NORMAL PEEKING.
- SO WHAT IS IT?

514
00:20:28,666 --> 00:20:30,916
- HEALTH AND P.E.
PRACTICAL TRAINING.

515
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:31,875
- SUMMON!

516
00:20:36,250 --> 00:20:37,500
- SUMMON!

517
00:20:39,250 --> 00:20:41,791
KEEP GOING, AKI.
I'LL TAKE CARE OF THIS ONE.

518
00:20:41,875 --> 00:20:44,125
- GOOD LUCK, KOUTA.

519
00:20:44,208 --> 00:20:47,000
NOW IT'S ALL UP TO ME!

520
00:20:47,083 --> 00:20:48,333
I'LL MAKE IT.

521
00:20:48,416 --> 00:20:50,500
FOR THE GUYS!

522
00:20:50,583 --> 00:20:52,333
( gasps )

523
00:20:52,416 --> 00:20:54,375
NO...

524
00:20:54,458 --> 00:20:56,958
IT'S IRON MAN.

525
00:20:57,041 --> 00:20:58,750
- PATHETIC.

526
00:20:58,833 --> 00:21:01,041
ARE YOU BOYS EVER GONNA LEARN
HOW TO STAY OUT OF TROUBLE?

527
00:21:01,125 --> 00:21:03,791
- PROBABLY NOT. BUT I DON'T
HAVE TIME TO TALK ABOUT IT!

528
00:21:03,875 --> 00:21:07,583
SUMMON!
- ( grunting )

529
00:21:07,666 --> 00:21:10,583
- WAIT, YOU DIDN'T SUMMON
YOUR AVATAR, MR. NISHIMURA.

530
00:21:10,666 --> 00:21:13,208
- IT'S A LONG STORY, BUT I
DON'T ACTUALLY HAVE A SCORE.

531
00:21:13,291 --> 00:21:15,666
- WELL, ISN'T THAT FANCY.
ALL RIGHTY THEN...

532
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:18,666
GET READY!
DIE, IRON MAN!

533
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:21,083
- ( grunts )
- WHAT?!

534
00:21:21,166 --> 00:21:25,333
- YOSHII, I SHOULD REVOKE
YOUR SUMMONING PRIVILEGES,

535
00:21:25,416 --> 00:21:26,208
BUT I WON'T.

536
00:21:26,291 --> 00:21:28,083
YOU WANNA KNOW WHY?
- MAYBE.

537
00:21:28,166 --> 00:21:30,666
- I LIKE THAT YOU'RE
A PROBATIONARY STUDENT.

538
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:33,291
'CAUSE AS LONG AS
IT'S JUST AN AVATAR,

539
00:21:33,375 --> 00:21:36,166
I DON'T HAVE TO FEEL BAD
ABOUT DOING THIS.

540
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:37,791
CLENCH YOUR TEETH, KIDDO!

541
00:21:37,875 --> 00:21:39,375
- ( Avatar screams )

542
00:21:39,458 --> 00:21:41,375
- ( both scream )

543
00:21:41,458 --> 00:21:45,583
- PRESUMPTUOUS IDIOTS 
TAKE A REMEDIAL CLASS.

544
00:21:45,666 --> 00:21:47,500
THAT'S YOU THREE, BY THE WAY.

545
00:21:47,583 --> 00:21:49,583
- ( all groaning )

546
00:21:49,666 --> 00:21:52,458
- THUS THE FIRST DAY OF
TRAINING CAMP COMES TO AN END.

547
00:21:52,541 --> 00:21:53,916
AKIHISA AND HIS FRIENDS
HAVE YET TO BE CLEARED

548
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:56,416
OF THE ACCUSATIONS
AGAINST THEM.

549
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:59,875
WHAT WILL HAPPEN NEXT? WILL THE
EVER FIND THE BLACKMAILER?

550
00:21:59,958 --> 00:22:02,041
( flatly )
BUM BUM BUM.

551
00:22:07,125 --> 00:22:09,916
- ( singing in Japanese )

552
00:23:34,875 --> 00:23:36,625
- Yuuji:
BAKA AND TEST!

553
00:23:43,083 --> 00:23:45,333
- I'M SO RELAXED.
I'M LIKE A PUDDLE.

554
00:23:45,416 --> 00:23:48,291
- YEAH, I ALWAYS FEEL LIKE THAT
AFTER A LONG BATH.

555
00:23:49,916 --> 00:23:51,250
- ( beeps )

556
00:23:51,333 --> 00:23:53,208
- Fukuhara:
QUESTION SIX--

557
00:23:53,291 --> 00:23:55,208
"HISTORY REPEATS ITSELF."

558
00:23:55,291 --> 00:23:57,208
PROVIDE AN EXAMPLE
OF THIS ADAGE.

559
00:23:57,291 --> 00:23:59,208
- Hideyoshi:
REINCARNATION?

560
00:23:59,291 --> 00:24:01,416
- YOU GONNA BE IN CLASS "F"
IN YOUR NEXT LIFE TOO?

561
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:03,833
- Akihisa: NEXT EPISODE: ME,
PEEKING AND GUYS' FRIENDSHIP!

562
00:24:03,916 --> 00:24:06,125
- Fukuhara:
THIS WILL BE ON THE TEST.

